entry.string: SELECT country_code, country_name FROM weather.cities city left join countries country on city.country=country.country_code where country_code is not null group by city.country;
SELECT country_code, country_name FROM weather.cities city left join countries country on city.country=country.country_code group by city.country;

SELECT country_code, country_name FROM weather.cities city left join countries country on city.country=country.country_code where country_code is not null group by city.country order by country_code ASC;
